### Critical Issue:
**Backend server was DOWN** due to syntax error I introduced:
```
PathError [TypeError]: Missing parameter name at index 1: *
at backend/server.js:145 - app.options('*', cors())
```

### Fix Applied:
- ‚ùå REMOVED: Broken `app.options('*', cors())` line
- ‚úÖ KEPT: Main CORS configuration (already handles OPTIONS)
